<div class="content"><nav class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › Warranty</nav><h1>Wrap Warranty</h1><p class="lead speakable">Every fleet wrap from Chicago Fleet Wraps includes a 2-year workmanship warranty plus manufacturer material warranties from Avery Dennison and 3M.</p><h2>Workmanship Warranty — 2 Years</h2><ul><li>Covers lifting, peeling, bubbling, or edge failure due to installation</li><li>Free repair or replacement of affected panels</li><li>Applies to all fleet wraps installed by our team</li></ul><h2>Material Warranty — 5–7 Years</h2><ul><li><strong>Avery Dennison MPI 1105:</strong> 7-year outdoor vertical durability</li><li><strong>3M IJ180-CV3:</strong> 5-year outdoor vertical durability</li><li><strong>DOL 1360 overlaminate:</strong> UV and scratch protection rated to match film life</li><li>Covers fading, cracking, and delamination under normal conditions</li></ul><h2>What's Not Covered</h2><ul><li>Damage from collisions, accidents, or vandalism</li><li>Brush car wash or high-pressure washer damage</li><li>Chemical exposure (solvents, fuel spills, harsh degreasers)</li><li>Normal wear on high-contact areas (door handles, step rails)</li></ul><div class="cta-bar"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/estimate/">Get a Free Estimate →</a><a class="btn" href="tel:+13125971286" style="border-color:#F5C518;color:#F5C518">📞 (312) 597-1286</a></div></div>